    "grammar_explanation": "本句为并列复合句，由连词\"and\"连接两个主句。第一个主句\"AI models generate responses and outputs based on complex algorithms and machine learning techniques\"以\"AI models\"为主语，\"generate\"为谓语动词，\"responses and outputs\"为并列宾语，\"based on...\"为过去分词短语作状语，修饰宾语的来源依据。第二个主句\"those responses or outputs may be inaccurate, harmful, biased or indecent\"以\"those responses or outputs\"为主语，\"may be\"为情态动词短语作谓语，后接四个并列形容词作表语，表示可能存在的负面特征。",
